{
  "stem": "16930.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they had the-- they-- they claimed they had a lot of fun there, a lot of girls there, and a lot of parties, it was fun, to induce people to join the youth movement of the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And of course, being in B'nai Akiva, having that ideology, and knowing that-- that the Communists were against godliness, did not believe in God, I didn't join them, fortunately.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But there were certainly enough inducements.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I also began to read.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to-- my first thing whenever I went to a new neighborhood was to get a library card.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I also was beginning to buy books.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In where I worked in this diamond thing then, in Manhattan Island, they were selling books, second-hand books off barrels-- off barrels-- you know that barrels?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were selling secondhand books for sixpence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was buying these secondhand books on political science and sociology and different political books and reading them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and so I got a little bit of education out of it-- a little bit of informal education out of it, and-- because my formal education only went to 8th grade in a village school, public school.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got a little bit education out of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I also became-- began to hunger for education.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and then subsequently, when I went on hakhshara, we-- that was in Buckinghamshire, in-- in a town called Buckingham.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had-- and again, it was possibly because we lived in-- in a couple of housing-- housing there-- housing units there-- huts there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were used by the Minister of Agriculture to house women agricultural workers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then they put us into them, men and women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we used to go out to work for different farmers.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
